            <title>[MNG-2809] Can&apos;t activate a profile by checking for the presence of a file in ${user.home}</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MNG-2809</link>
                <project id="12316922" key="MNG">Maven (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following won&apos;t activate. If I move it to a path without a space it works. This is for windows xp.&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;file&amp;gt;&amp;lt;exists&amp;gt;${user.home}/.m2/ydoc/lib/ydoc.jar&amp;lt;/exists&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/file&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
