                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14411132" author="mdproctor" created="Sun, 4 Feb 2007 18:06:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Actually I&apos;m not sure if this is spaces. I tried it using ${basedir} with a path that didn&apos;t have spaces, it iddn&apos;t activate. I looked at the help:effective-pom and cut and pasted the whole url it was displaying there and it worked. Does that mean that profiles are being decided before the variable resolving is done?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14411044" author="wsmoak" created="Sun, 4 Feb 2007 18:32:36 +0000"  >
&lt;p&gt;This works:    &amp;lt;file&amp;gt;&amp;lt;exists&amp;gt;c:/Documents and Settings/wsmoak/file.txt&amp;lt;/exists&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/file&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This doesn&apos;t:  &amp;lt;file&amp;gt;&amp;lt;exists&amp;gt;${user.home}/file.txt&amp;lt;/exists&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/file&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14412441" author="siveton" created="Tue, 8 Jan 2008 07:45:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed with r609976&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14414642" author="danpfe" created="Wed, 4 Mar 2009 09:30:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Still does not work (Maven 2.0.10) with ${basedir} as described in the related issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14414493" author="ID134349" created="Wed, 4 Mar 2009 22:50:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Daniel, can you please provide a ZIP of the most basic project to demonstrate this error? &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14414655" author="brettporter" created="Wed, 4 Mar 2009 22:55:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Paul, it&apos;s in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MNG-3017&quot; title=&quot;Profile activation by file fails when maven is run outside the pom&amp;#39;s directory&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MNG-3017&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MNG-3017&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14414514" author="brettporter" created="Wed, 4 Mar 2009 22:57:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;note that it is not a regression, it does work with ${user.home}&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17998201" author="JIRAUSER302100" created="Sat, 5 Jul 2025 13:03:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This project has moved from Jira to GitHub Issues. This issue was migrated to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven/issues/4920&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;apache/maven#4920&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
